commit.message:
Undef HAVE_POSIX_SHM and HAVE_POSIX_TIMER

For compatibility with old distros

Support OCaml 5

- Import MR to build with OCaml 5: https://gitlab.com/gerdstolpmann/lib-ocamlnet3/-/merge_requests/21#d4966c37d799aad776d7e8a903d5c02d7641de69
- Fix remaining warnings

Update Drive generated service.

Workaround for issues: astrada/google-drive-ocamlfuse#805,
astrada/google-drive-ocamlfuse#807

Update upload method in service generator

Align the upload URL to the docs (https://developers.google.com/drive/api/guides/manage-uploads#resumable).
The official upload URL is: https://www.googleapis.com/upload/drive/v3/files?uploadType=resumable
While in the discovery document is still:
"resumable": {
  "multipart": true,
  "path": "/resumable/upload/drive/v3/files"
}

commit.message:
Do not silence deprecation warnings

`Yojson.Safe.json` was deprecated a long time ago and is going to be
removed now. Silencing the deprecation has the downside that authors are
unaware that this is happening.
